                <note rend="inline" type="source">791.003/92: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Philip</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1928-04-16T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 16, 1928—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>31. Your 39, April 13, 8 p.m. Please telegraph at once brief summary of new
                    arbitration law and indicate the character of civil suits which it is proposed
                    to submit for settlement thereunder.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Kellogg</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
